        public EDIFCellInstance getCellInstanceFromHierName(java.lang.String name)
        Based on a hierarchical string, this method will get the instance corresponding to the name provided.
        Parameters:
        name - Hierarchical name of the instance, for example: 'clk_wiz/inst/bufg0'
        Returns:
        The instance corresponding to the provided name. If the name string is empty, it returns the top cell instance.

        Parameters:

        public java.util.Set<EDIFAbsoluteCellInstance> getAllLeafDecendants(java.lang.String instanceName)

        Parameters:

        Returns:
